members.name: getColor
members.comment: Gets the color of this object. This may be null to represent the default color of an object, if the object has a special default color (e.g Shulkers).

members.name: setColor
members.comment: Sets the color of this object to the specified DyeColor. This may be null to represent the default color of an object, if the object has a special default color (e.g Shulkers).

param: color - The color of the object, as a DyeColor.
throws: NullPointerException - if argument is null and this implementation does not support null

name: org.bukkit.material.Colorable
comment: An object that can be colored.
